message.1
	Sorry I can't do that
message.2
	I see I was put to bed. Its AFternoon & I overslept!
message.3
	Welcome to ADVEWNTURE: 5 `THE COUNT`. Dedicated to Alvin Files.\n
message.4
	I'm up in A cAstle, in the distAnce I see VOODOO CASTLE. There'sstAnding room outside the window
message.5
	Some time passes...
message.6
	It bears the Family Crest of DRACULA!
message.7
	Tell me to what? i.e. `TO TREE`
message.8
	higher
message.9
	I hear the
message.10
	Flagpole splinter
message.11
	of you always asking for help!
message.12
	I fall to my death
message.13
	How?
message.14
	I've turned into A VAMPIRE!
message.15
	I think I can only take
message.16
	more days of this!
message.17
	I appear pale & drained!
message.18
	My neck looks BITTEN!
message.19
	Its getting DARK outside!
message.20
	I'm getting very tired
message.21
	The sun has set!
message.22
	TODAY I look healthy...
message.23
	A bAt flew by & LAUGHED At me!
message.24
	I'm real PEPPY now!
message.25
	There's A COUGHIN (sic) in the room.
message.26
	COUGH!
message.27
	The cigArette went out & the coffin VANISHED
message.28
	He smelled something & flew on
message.29
	he settled on my NECK!
message.30
	Sheet came untied
message.31
	Strange watch says
message.32
	moves till sunset
message.33
	I closed the lid and I suffocated!
message.34
	Its LOCKED from INSIDE!
message.35
	There's something there, maybe I should
message.36
	go there?
message.37
	empty it?
message.38
	I see nothing special.
message.39
	OK
message.40
	There's A tremendous Amount of HEAT & SUNLIGHT coming out.
message.41
	DeAr DRACKY, Don't open this present till HALLOWEEN.\nsigned COUNT YORGA.
message.42
	\nA bell rings somewhere: `DING-DONG`.\n
message.43
	Peasants attack me, I was SUPPOSED to destroy the VAMPIRE!
message.44
	YOU HAVE LOST!
message.45
	Its for DRACULA, its and EATING & GHOULING bill from a\nlocal mortuary!
message.46
	There's a note PAPER CLIPPED to the postcard
message.47
	Postmaster says he'll be delivering a package tomorrow.
message.48
	I don't know where to look
message.49
	I drive the stake through his HEART. The townspeople\ncome and carry me off cheering! (Don't worry, I tell them I\nowe it all to you!!!!)
message.50
	Try: `CLIMB SHEET`
message.51
	I'm A pretty good LOCK PICK!
message.52
	I'm not an arsonist!
message.53
	The torch burnt thru the sheet!
message.54
	Ah that's much better!
message.55
	There's writing on it.
message.56
	Mob looks ANGRY
message.57
	I've a hunch I've been robbed!
message.58
	Odd, I wasn't bitten last nite!
message.59
	Nothing happens.
message.60
	lower
message.61
	I'm At the tip of the pole
message.62
	I notice a DARK WINDOW UNDER the bedroom window ledge!
message.63
	as I fall
message.64
	EXCEPT
message.65
	It won't go any
message.66
	try looking at it
message.67
	The paper clip is in the way!
message.68
	I know how to RAISE and LOWER this thing!
message.69
	GET UP you sleepy head!
message.70
	Try examining things.
message.71
	I've no matches!
message.72
	The match flares up briefly ...
message.73
	Its already open.
message.74
	Try: `CLIMB POLE`
message.75
	Try: `SAVE GAME`
message.76
	A bat might make it, but not me!
message.77
	First I need an unlit cigarette.
message.78
	Tell me with what? Like: `WITH FIST`
message.79
	It doesn't work!
message.80
	Maybe I should BREAK it?
message.81
	Yuck!
message.82
	and then goes out!
message.83
	Mirror shatters! That's 7 years bad luck!
message.84
	I set the mirror on the pillow.
message.85
	Try: `GO ROOM`
message.86
	What a DREAM I just had !!!!
message.87
	Dear Adventurer:\nI wanted to take this time (1 move!) to thank ALL of you out\nthere in ADventureland for the fantastically warm reception\nAdventure has received!\nHappy Adventuring,\nScott Adams\n(Chief Adventurer)
message.88
	A choooooo
